            </div>
            <div class="resource-card">
                <h3>🎨 HTML Living Standard</h3>
                <p>Current HTML specification</p>
                <a href="https://html.spec.whatwg.org/" target="_blank">whatwg.org</a>
            </div>
            <div class="resource-card">
                <h3>🏗️ HTML5 Doctor</h3>
                <p>Semantic HTML reference</p>
