                    <h3>New Semantic Elements</h3>
                    <p>HTML5 introduced many new semantic elements for better structure.</p>
                    
                    <div class="html-block">
<span class="tag">&lt;header&gt;</span>    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Page/section header --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;nav&gt;</span>       <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Navigation --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;main&gt;</span>       <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Main content --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;article&gt;</span>   <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Self-contained --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;section&gt;</span>   <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Thematic group --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;aside&gt;</span>      <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Sidebar content --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;footer&gt;</span>    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Page/section footer --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;figure&gt;</span>     <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Media with caption --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;details&gt;</span>   <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Expandable --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;mark&gt;</span>       <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Highlighted text --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;time&gt;</span>       <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Date/time --&gt;</span>
                    </div>

                    <h3>New Form Input Types</h3>
                    <p>HTML5 added many new input types with built-in validation.</p>
                    
                    <div class="html-block">
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"email"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>      <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Email --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"url"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>       <span class="comment">&lt;!-- URL --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"tel"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>       <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Phone --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"search"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Search --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"number"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>     <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Number --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"range"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>     <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Slider --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"color"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>     <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Color picker --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"date"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>      <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Date --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"time"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>      <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Time --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"datetime-local"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span> <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Date+time --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"week"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>      <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Week --&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"month"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>     <span class="comment">&lt;!-- Month --&gt;</span>
                    </div>

                    <h3>Form Validation</h3>
                    <p>HTML5 provides built-in form validation without JavaScript.</p>
                    
                    <div class="html-block">
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">required</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"email"</span> <span class="attr">multiple</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">pattern</span>=<span class="string">"[0-9]{5}"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">min</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attr">max</span>=<span class="string">"100"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">minlength</span>=<span class="string">"3"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
                    </div>

                    <h3>DataList</h3>
                    <p>Provides autocomplete suggestions for inputs.</p>
                    
                    <div class="html-block">
<span class="tag">&lt;input</span> <span class="attr">list</span>=<span class="string">"browsers"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;datalist</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"browsers"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
    <span class="tag">&lt;option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">"Chrome"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
    <span class="tag">&lt;option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">"Firefox"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
    <span class="tag">&lt;option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">"Safari"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
<span class="tag">&lt;/datalist&gt;</span>
                    </div>

                    <h3>ContentEditable</h3>
                    <p>Make any element editable by users.</p>
                    
                    <div class="html-block">
<span class="tag">&lt;div</span> <span class="attr">contenteditable</span>=<span class="string">"true"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
    Click to edit this text!
<span class="tag">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
                    </div>

                    <h3>Local Storage</h3>
                    <p>Store data in the browser without a database.</p>
                    
                    <div class="html-block">
<span class="comment">&lt;!-- Store data --&gt;</span>
localStorage.setItem('username', 'alice');

<span class="comment">&lt;!-- Retrieve data --&gt;</span>
localStorage.getItem('username');

<span class="comment">&lt;!-- Remove data --&gt;</span>
localStorage.removeItem('username');
                    </div>

                    <h3>Drag and Drop</h3>
                    
                    <div class="html-block">
<span class="tag">&lt;div</span> <span class="attr">draggable</span>=<span class="string">"true"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>Drag me!<span class="tag">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
                    </div>
                `,
                quiz: [
